Rating: 3
This has an outstanding sweet, sour, salt balance. I do not recommend reducing the sugar. I served this with Filipino Style London Broil (excellent) and they complimented each other perfectly.

Rating: 4
I never thought I would be rating rice at four forks, but this rice is worthy. The vinegar and sugar give it an intriguing flavor. I serve this with Ginger Flank Steak with Sake-glazed Vegetables (recipe also from this web site).

