Rating: 4
This was a delicious and refreshing way to prepare rice. I only used 1/2 tbsp of sugar, and it was still excellent. I served it along with grilled chicken, and my husband raved about it. Will definately make again!

Rating: 4
This dish is delicious and I have made it numerous times, a personal favorite. I usually cook only for myself, so I cut the proportions from one cup of rice to between 1/4 and 1/2 cup, but I use the same amount of the vinegar solution. I also add about a teaspoon of salt to the boiling water of the rice, and usually forget to cook it on high heat for the last minute, and I can't tell the difference.